{"tid":1882202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本的肺炎陰謀（人口老化清洗計劃）","createTime":"2020-02-16T05:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T09:20:26.000Z","uid":121126,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd577c73ad39419fd1a3f9179d45f57f2141e57","tid":1882202,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"日本人口老化越來越嚴重！有數據統計，2060年日本的人口將減少近3分之1，甚至當時有40％人口將達到65歲以上，讓75歲老人仍需外出求職，恐成為常態。<br />\n<br />\n以社會經濟發展黎講，年輕既人係經濟發展時主力，因為最願意消費既人群，因為係發達地區gdp主要係第3產業，而年輕人擔當主力，<br />\n<br />\n而老人不從事經濟生產，反而對社會經濟同福利做成負擔，老年化會清耗更多福利，導致稅務增加，令到社會消費意欲降低，從而惡性循環減低gdp增長，年輕人負擔加重，降低生育意欲，最終加劇人口老化，宜家日本被人口老化拖入左泥潭<br />\n<br />\n難得宜家有一個病毒可以清除老齡人，而對年輕人傷害較低，一個完美清洗日本人口老化方法<br />\n雖然可能會陣痛，例如影響東京奧運，但可以將日本從泥潭拉出黎，百年國運比小小奧運重要無數倍"},{"pid":"06988fb45a31bb1906d0899f980f53e08c0b3fda","tid":1882202,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0762768d90272a57c827687db0c426d5a4c4a3c","tid":1882202,"uid":178800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"怪錯安倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2998a685bbd5b57717452b86c0ee1123a9830127","tid":1882202,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0762768d90272a57c827687db0c426d5a4c4a3c","tid":1882202,"uid":178800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"怪錯安倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=